HEADWORD: Acnode
<hw>Ac"node</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>acus</ets>
needle + E. <ets>node</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Geom.)</fld> <def>An isolated
